    {
        "content": "<p>You can say <code>n ^ n - n = n (n-1) n^(n-2)</code> and <code>n! = n (n - 1) (n - 2)!</code>, and then you can get the result from <code>(n-2)! ≤ (n-2)^(n-2) ≤ n^(n-2)</code></p>",
        "id": 485879140,
        "sender_full_name": "Daniel Weber",
        "timestamp": 1733238972
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah but n^n - n is not n (n - 1) n^(n-2)</p>",
        "id": 485978928,
        "sender_full_name": "duck",
        "timestamp": 1733270480
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But I think I’ve got it thanks so much</p>",
